Manage Seller Account Amazon with Jenna Lieber

with Jenna Lieber of Turnkey Product Management

You’ll Learn

  • The most important prelude to working on Growing your Amazon business
  • How one strategy can transform your business (hint: it’s pretty widely used offline, too)
  • Which tools Jenna’s team uses to manage tasks
  • Her favourite Amazon tools
  • How to manage your budget

Next Steps

Free resources page – Turnkeyproductmanagement.com/resource
Book free break-through session call
– Agency
– Coaching etc.
– Physical product brands
– Typically minimum $250K a year
– FaceBook group – produced every week

Other interviews about Growing your Amazon business

Scaling your Amazon Business with Fernando Cruz

Scaling a  business on Amazon with Ashley Pearce of Future State Media

eCommerce Growth Strategy with Brad Moss of Product Labs

 

Watch Grow Amazon Business with Jenna Lieber
